name: Many-Fangs - Raptor Pack Alpha
text: 1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner "Raptor Pack" monsters/nThis card must be Synchro Summoned. If this card is targeted by an opponent’s card or effect or a card or effect is activated that would destroy this card: Negate that effect. You can target 1 "Raptor Pack" Synchro Monster in your GY and 1 face-up card your opponent controls; shuffle both targets back into their respective owner’s Decks. You can only activate this effect of "Many-Fangs - Raptor Pack Alpha" once per turn.
